Class NativeIdentifier

java.lang.Object
  gov.nih.nlm.meme.common.Identifier.Default
      gov.nih.nlm.meme.common.NativeIdentifier
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable, Identifier, Rankable
Direct Known Subclasses:
CodeSource, CodeTermgroup, CUISource
public class NativeIdentifier
extends Identifier.Default

This class represents an identifier expressed in terms the original source intended. This class represents an sg_id that uses a type of CODE_SOURCE or CODE_STRIPPED_SOURCE.

Author:
MEME Group
See Also:
